TruBridge™ Technology

			
Fit Gets Personal

			
With our revolutionary new frame fitting system, a perfect fit is easy, so you can choose whatever style you want and not worry about how it will feel. TruBridge™ Technology adapts the frame to the width and depth of your nose bridge, so you never have to pass up a style you love.

		

	


	

		

			
			
			
			
			
		

	







	

		

			
The Science Behind An Optimized Fit

			
Oakley TruBridge™ Technology uses interchangeable nosepads to adapt the fit perfectly, so the frame performs best for you.

		

	


	

		

			
			
Maximum Pad Contact

		

		

			
			
No Cheek Contact

		

		

			
			
Centered Line Of Sight

		

	







	

		

			
One Frame. Four Fits.

			
With four nosepad sizes to customize the fit, the frame is optimized for multiple nose bridge shapes.

		

	



	

		

			
		

			
					

						
						
Size 1

					


			
					

						
						
Size 2

					


			
					

						
						
Size 3

					


			
					

						
						
Size 4

					


					


		

	


	

		
		

		
		

		
		

		
		

		
		
		

	

			
			

				

					
					
Size 1

					
High Bridge

					
Smallest pad area for those with a high bridge and more surface area.

				

			

		

			
			

				

					
					
Size 2

					
Medium Bridge

					
Average pad area - the most common size for medium nose bridges.

				

			

		

			
			

				

					
					
Size 3

					
Narrow Bridge

					
Larger pad area provides additional support for narrower nose bridges.

				

			

		

			
			

				

					
					
Size 4

					
Shallow Bridge

					
Largest pad area intended for wearers with a shallow nose bridge and the lease surface area.

				

			

		










	

	

	

		

			
Premium Materials

						
Built with the Best

						

								
Metal

								
O Matter

							

						
Select frames are made with lightweight O Matter™, a durable performance material with the comfort and impact resistance of controlled flexibility. It doesn’t deform over time like acetate but it’s twice as strong, yet 25% lighter.
